snippet.title: Amber Heard Blasted For Awkwardly Flubbing Darren Criss' Name At The 2019 Golden Globes
snippet.description:
Amber Heard made a major oops onstage at the 2019 Golden Globes on Sunday when she flubbed Darren Criss' name while presenting the award for Best Actor in a Limited Series. Watch for more on viewers' reaction to her awkward slip-up!
